Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  心情不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算駕駛技術再好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也別開得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水沒忘記關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:05:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾  今天也一早就去礦場了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上樓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(646.5,969)\fs54}Giftdium
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東邊的天賜礦石礦脈  果然下去看看是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是由於時間久遠而變色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  反應相差很大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到證據了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽所說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你的午餐時間要用的麵包  拿來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我現在就去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觀測到利瑪的異常活性  是在今天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐標是乙6207
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處在靛藍花園的最深部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部署去那的是哪個部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是斯圖爾特大尉的小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白的吧  大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千萬不要有什麼多餘的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常明白  中校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像聽到的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  按照剛才吩咐的帶上裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照剛才吩咐的分散作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照剛才吩咐的開始作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  下水時安全最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Otter One 確認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1089,969)\fs54}下潛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始DIVE IN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2  DIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3  DIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  這就是之前預約好的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  這個奶油麵包是附送的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾  宗吾  宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我向多蒙問聲好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐時間  也許趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  又這樣橫衝直撞亂開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:09:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等等  佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點開起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在試穿婚紗的時候逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直豈有此理  佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚紗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是父母間擅自定下的婚約
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚約？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得這種做法很陳舊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不講理了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陳舊也好  不講理也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是瓦洛夫家的規定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是正確之路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那誰來顧我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要有私人感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要考慮兩家的繁榮就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻不傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是這麼覺得的吧  宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你教唆佳音這麼做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管他們  加速
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還欸什麼欸啊
