Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾  這個女孩剛剛是從石頭裏出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不像呢…
